  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend from Candyland! - Tower Defense Sweetness!</h2><br><i>Immerse yourself in the ultimate tower defense experience! Can you withstand the sugary assault and rise to the top of the leaderboard?</i><br><br><strong>Gripping Story:</strong><br>Immerse yourself in the tale of Eden's struggle against the sour onslaught from Candyland. Uncover the mystery behind the invasion and meet intriguing characters along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/351b45151451a38fa1fbc11c1bbc0a93.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/351b45151451a38fa1fbc11c1bbc0a93.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/351b45151451a38fa1fbc11c1bbc0a93.mp4?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Interactive Tutorial with Dr. Dexter:</strong><br>Learn from the best! Dr. Dexter's new interactive tutorial will guide you through all essential mechanics and strategies, whether you're a new player or a seasoned defender.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0f62f9088e44e4e7af67ece5eb2ce974.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0f62f9088e44e4e7af67ece5eb2ce974.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0f62f9088e44e4e7af67ece5eb2ce974.mp4?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Plant Your Defense!:</strong><br>Plant trees to battle the sour candies and Defend from Candyland! Strategize and construct your ultimate defense setup.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/b0f7f6d7c47edac12a5ba78c3c766064.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/b0f7f6d7c47edac12a5ba78c3c766064.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Path-Shaping Mastery:</strong><br>Bend the enemy's path with cleverly positioned trees. Slow down and divert the relentless candy invaders. Every twist and turn affects the outcome.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/8ae7e1b116d653c8bf6b61ce8cf1f387.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/8ae7e1b116d653c8bf6b61ce8cf1f387.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/8ae7e1b116d653c8bf6b61ce8cf1f387.mp4?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Shop Smart, Defend Better:</strong><br>Enhance your defences by buying trees, buffs, and items that reveal enemy paths. Build a formidable defense with smart purchases.<br><br><strong>Evolving Defenses:</strong><br>Nurture and upgrade your trees as you master the art of tower defense. Adapt to evolving challenges and crush the candy invaders.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0b1a790bd7a33c5408bef339edff4219.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0b1a790bd7a33c5408bef339edff4219.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/0b1a790bd7a33c5408bef339edff4219.mp4?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Endless Mode Showdown:</strong><br>Test your skills in Endless Mode, complete with a public leaderboard. Can you reach the top?<br><br><strong>Triumph Over Sugary Foes:</strong><br>Face waves of candies of all sizes. Each has its own weakness. Can you outsmart them all?<br><br><strong>Challenging Levels:</strong><br>Take on 120 meticulously designed levels. The battle for Eden has just begun!<br><br><strong>Unique Towers:</strong><br>Discover a delightful range of tower types. Crush the candy invaders with the Peashooter, Cherry Bomb, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/b50c22a3d80419403084a9ed887d702c.avif?t=1757865443\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/f38b12e9a86e61052de19c0871b78e71.avif?t=1757865443\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><br><strong>Meet Eden's Guardians:</strong><br>Engage with the charming residents of Eden. Get to know Oracle Tree, Mrs. Applebee, and others!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/a37c0f37152f849cd8287c372c6ca382.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/a37c0f37152f849cd8287c372c6ca382.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/b2aee16cb3f06b2788561956344f06c1.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/b2aee16cb3f06b2788561956344f06c1.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Top-Notch Pixel Art:</strong><br>Enjoy stunning pixel art. Eden comes to life with every tree, candy, and character.<br><br><strong>Incredible Soundtrack:</strong><br>Experience an enchanting soundtrack by Arman Mkhitaryan.<br><br><strong>Enhanced Visuals and Health Bars:</strong><br>Enjoy updated visuals and improved health bar positioning for a more immersive experience.<br><br><strong>Steam Store Art:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/fc66742b87ce3461050ccc7c6849d291.avif?t=1757865443\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br>Millie Elsdon-James's art sets the stage for your candy-crushing adventure. <br><br><strong>Challenge Your Wits:</strong><br>Can you outsmart the candies as they grow in strength and numbers? Overcome ever-changing challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/e6d611adcc45f419ae165e3d9eac7d9e.poster.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/e6d611adcc45f419ae165e3d9eac7d9e.webm?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/e6d611adcc45f419ae165e3d9eac7d9e.mp4?t=1757865443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Your Destiny Awaits:</strong><br>Build your towers and unleash your tower defense prowess. Defend Eden from the candy onslaught. Are you up for the challenge? Can you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800480/extras/c65e5b7285fe91d80161b3dc7a984a6a.avif?t=1757865443\" width=600 height=262 /></span>",
